highlights.text: “零距离的思念” by TINY 7 has been on Viral Songs Malaysia the longest, at 143 days straight.
Anirudh Ravichander has the most spots on Viral Songs Malaysia. “Kokki” is the highest at #21.
“Bintang (Original Version)” by Budak Kacamata is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Malaysia, up 21 spots at #67.
“Rindu Pelukmu” by Chaeroel and 4Loven is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Malaysia at #94.
